Author: Aliaksandr Abushkevich 
------------------------------------------------------
This package consists of two parts: server and client.

SERVER
Server was packaged as plugin to twistd

CLIENT
Client application was developed using GTK2.0. 
It is known to work under Ubuntu 9.04/GNOME.
Application was not tested on Windows OS.


To run server and client, execute

>>python run_all.py

------------------------------------------------------
